n Carlisle, Cumberland, England":"英国波藍德斯泰頓 在 卡萊爾","Whitrigg, Cumberland, England":"英国波藍德特利格","of Great Orton, Cumberland, England":"英国英格兰波藍德格亞特 奧爾頓","lifeSummary":"Joan Orton是Giles Orton of Stainton和Maud的女儿，于1345年出生。她于1369年9月之前与Sir Clement Skelton MP结婚。他们至少是1个儿子和3个女儿的父母。她去世于1414年在英国享年69岁。"},"hr":{"1345–1414":"1345.–1414.","1352–Female":"1352–preminula","1354–Female":"1354–preminula","1345–1399":"1345.–1399","1370–1439":"1370.–1439","1372–1412":"1372.–1412.","1380–1450":"1380–1450","–1450":"–1450","1310–1369":"1310–1369","–Female":"preminula","before 1345":"prije 1345.","1352":"1352","1450":"1450","1372":"1372.","1382":"1382","1370":"1370.","1380":"1380","3 August 1369":"3. kolovoza 1369.","before September 1369":"prije rujna 1369.","1414":"1414.","1369":"1369","1412":"1412.","1345":"1345.","1399":"1399","1310":"1310","1354":"1354","after 1399":"nakon 1399.","1439":"1439","ABT 1380":"oko 1380.","Hesket in the Forest, Cumberland, England":"Hesket in the Forest, Cumberland, England","England":"England","Stainton in Carlisle, Cumberland, England":"Stainton in Carlisle, Cumberland, England","Whitrigg, Cumberland, England":"Whitrigg, Cumberland, England","of Great Orton, Cumberland, England":"Great Orton, Cumberland, Engleska, United Kingdom"},"cs":{"1345–1414":"1345–1414","1352–Female":"1352–Zesnulá","1354–Female":"1354–Zesnulá","1345–1399":"1345–1399","1370–1439":"1370–1439","1372–1412":"1372–1412","1380–1450":"1380–1450","–1450":"–1450","1310–1369":"1310–1369","–Female":"Zesnulá","before 1345":"před 1345","1352":"1352","1450":"1450","1372":"1372","1382":"1382","1370":"1370","1380":"1380","3 August 1369":"3. srpna 1369","before September 1369":"před září 1369","1414":"1414","1369":"1369","1412":"1412","1345":"1345","1399":"1399","1310":"1310","1354":"1354","after 1399":"po 1399","1439":"1439","ABT 1380":"okolo 1380","Hesket in the Forest, Cumberland, England":"Hesket in the Forest, Cumberland, Anglie","England":"Anglie","Stainton in Carlisle, Cumberland, England":"Stain